'''Cameroon Cricket Association''' is the official [[Sport governing body|governing body]] of the sport of [[cricket]] in [[Cameroon]] and operates [[Cameroon national cricket team]]. Cameroon Cricket Association is Cameroon's representative at the [[International Cricket Council]] and is an affiliate member and has been a member of that body since 2007. It is also a member of the [[African Cricket Association]].

