'''Cardio lethwei''' is a [[sport]]-specific, equipment-based [[physical fitness|fitness]]. It uses the techniques of [[lethwei]] include, [[Punch (strike)|punches]], leg [[kicks]], [[knee]]s and [[elbow]]s.

