'''Carl Reindorf Park Stadium''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Dansoman]], a suburb of [[Accra]] in [[Ghana]].
== History == It used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home stadium of [[Liberty Professionals FC]]. The stadium holds 2,000 people. Formerly called Carl Reindorf Stadium, it is named in honour of the Ghanaian historian [[Carl Christian Reindorf]].
