'''Squadra Scappatella''' ({{UCI code|SCS}}) was a professional continental [[cycling team]] based in [[Austria]] and participated in professional [[cycling team]], which competed in elite [[road bicycle racing]] events such as the [[UCI Women's Road World Cup]].

In preparation for the 2009 season, the team merged with fellow Austrian squad: [[Team Uniqa]].<ref>http://www.cqranking.com/women/asp/gen/team.asp?year=2009&teamcode=TUE</ref><ref>http://www.cqranking.com/women/asp/gen/team.asp?year=2008&teamcode=UNG</ref>

