{{Other uses|Stadionul Orășenesc (disambiguation){{!}}Stadionul Orășenesc}} {{Infobox stadium | stadium_name = Stadionul Orășenesc | nickname = | image = | fullname = | location = [[Rîbnița]], [[Moldova]] | coordinates = {{coord|47.7745613|29.0043086|type:landmark}} | broke_ground = | built = | opened = | renovated = | expanded = | closed = | demolished = | owner = | operator = | surface = grass | construction_cost = | architect = | structural engineer = | services engineer = | general_contractor = | project_manager = | main_contractors = | former_names = | tenants = [[FC Iskra-Stali Rîbnița]] | seating_capacity = 4,500 | dimensions = | scoreboard = }} '''Stadionul Orășenesc''' ([[Russian language|Russian]]: '''Gorodskoi Stadion''') is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Rîbnița]], [[Moldova]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and served as the home for [[FC Iskra-Stali Rîbnița]] of the [[Moldovan National Division]]. The stadium has a capacity of 4,500 spectators.<ref>[https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2011/11/19/moldova/divizia-nationala/fc-iskra-stali-ribnita/fc-sheriff-tiraspol/1160236/venue/ Gorodskoi Stadion, Rîbniţa - Soccerway]</ref>
